name: Celestial Vigor #3
description: The tiger is a popular symbol in the Chinese culture, often used to represent strength and good health. In this abstract artwork, the tiger in the galactic clouds signifies these qualities. The bright colors and swirling patterns convey a sense of energy and movement, while the use of negative space allows the tiger to be the focal point of the piece. This artwork is a representation of the tiger's strength and energy, bringing good health and vitality to the viewer.
